<% layout('/layouts/boilerplate') %>

<div class="container my-5 fade-in">
  <div class="card shadow-lg border-0 rounded-4 p-4">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4 text-primary fw-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="lead">
      At <strong>SheSync</strong>, your privacy and trust are our top priorities. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal and health-related information.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4 text-secondary">1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
      <li class="list-group-item">Personal data: Name, age, email (if provided voluntarily).</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">Health-related data: Period dates, symptoms, cycle patterns, and wellness insights.</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">Non-identifiable data: App usage statistics, general device type, and feature engagement.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4 text-secondary">2. How We Use Your Data</h4>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
      <li class="list-group-item">To personalize health and cycle predictions tailored to your input.</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">To improve app performance, analytics, and user experience.</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">To notify you about important health reminders and app updates.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4 text-secondary">3. Data Protection</h4>
    <p>
      We use industry-standard encryption and secure storage practices to protect your data. Access is restricted to authorized personnel only.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4 text-secondary">4. Your Rights</h4>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
      <li class="list-group-item">You can request a copy of your data at any time.</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">You have the right to correct or update your personal information.</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">You may request complete data deletion by contacting us.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4 text-secondary">5. Sharing and Third Parties</h4>
    <p>
      We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal or health data with any third parties for marketing or advertising purposes.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4 text-secondary">6. Updates to This Policy</h4>
    <p>
      We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage users to review this page periodically. Continued use of the app implies acceptance of any changes made.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4 text-muted fst-italic">
      For any privacy-related concerns or requests, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@shesync.com">privacy@shesync.com</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
